 <div><strong>Before your event</strong> Complete this training module, including the Knowledge Check questions. Email a copy of your certificate to your Field Operations Manager or text it to <strong>301-926-6099</strong> <strong>Final Step:</strong> Schedule your training review call at <a href="https://uswellness.appointlet.com/s/eventreviewtraining" style="color:var(--usw-red);white-space:nowrap">[insert Appointlet link]</a> at least 3 days prior to your event.</div>
