 <li><strong>Read the room.</strong> Observe their body language and listen to what they say. Medical testing can be an uncomfortable experience for some people. Help participants feel at ease.</li>
 <li><strong>Social talk is not ok.</strong> Do not talk about personal matters, opinions, other assignments or anything else that is not related to the participant and the client having a positive and professional experience.</li>
 <li><strong>Dress code:</strong> Black scrubs, clean sneakers or clogs (no crocs).</li>
 </ul>

