 <tr><td><span class="tag-normal">≤ 5.6%</span></td><td>Normal</td><td>Encourage healthy lifestyle habits</td></tr>
 <tr><td><span class="tag-warn">5.7 – 6.4%</span></td><td>Pre-Diabetes Risk</td><td>Lifestyle counseling; encourage physician follow-up</td></tr>
